OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine though locally frosty
OL,6,Fstart in the south. A band of cloud
OL,7,Fand increasingly patchy rain moving
OL,8,Fsoutheastwards across England and
OL,9,FWales. Sunnier skies to the northwest,
OL,10,Fbut with showers, some heavy. Cool,
OL,11,Fwith blustery winds in the northwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPatchy rain clearing from
OL,14,Fsoutheast England, then chilly with
OL,15,Fclear periods in the south this
OL,16,Fevening. However, blustery showers in
OL,17,Fthe northwest becoming increasingly
OL,18,Fwidespread overnight, some heavy and
OL,19,Fthundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
